<h3><span id=".C5.92uvres_po.C3.A9tiques"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Œuvres_poétiques">Œuvres poétiques</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Jean-François_Marmontel&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=14" title="Modifier la section : Œuvres poétiques" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor"><span>modifier</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Jean-François_Marmontel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Modifier le code source de la section : Œuvres poétiques"><span>modifier le code</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
